Open the cabinet and get the salt shaker from the cabinet

high_descs: Turn to your left and walk towards the windows, then make a right and walk to the microwave.
Pick up the salt from the top, right cabinet, above the microwave.
Turn to your left and go to the drawers on your left, between the oven and dishwasher.
Place the salt in the middle drawer.
Turn to your right and go to the cabinets above the coffee maker.
Pick up the salt from the top, left cabinet.
Turn to your left and go back to the drawers, on your left, between the stove and the dishwasher.
Place the salt in the middle drawer, to the right of the other salt.
anns.task_desc: Put two containers of salt in the kitchen drawer.
